            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "比亞迪內地銷量下跌  王傳福指技術不夠領先",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">比亞迪(01211) 今年在國內市場的銷量下跌，董事長兼總裁王傳福在臨時股東大會表示，目前技術不夠領先，後面還將有重磅技術發布。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他認為，比亞迪國內銷量下滑，一方面由於公司目前技術領先度不及前幾年，技術成果的市場驚艷度下降，加上行業同質化特徵漸顯，另一方面，低溫充電速度慢等用戶需求痛點，也待通過技術突破予以解決。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他指，比亞迪的核心競爭力在於技術，公司旗下12萬工程師團隊，是公司後續技術攻堅、重塑領先優勢的關鍵底氣和支撐。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15482863-%e6%af%94%e4%ba%9e%e8%bf%aa%e5%85%a7%e5%9c%b0%e9%8a%b7%e9%87%8f%e4%b8%8b%e8%b7%8c-%e7%8e%8b%e5%82%b3%e7%a6%8f%e6%8c%87%e6%8a%80%e8%a1%93%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a0%e9%a0%98%e5%85%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/20250704_FI_source-ap_01211-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 15:35:28",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "A股午後升幅擴大   深股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股午後顯著向上，深股升逾1%，兩市成交合計17257.71億元(人民幣‧下同)。滬股一周計升14點，深股升逾1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-16.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數全日收報3902，升27點或0.08%，今早開報3873.12點，跌0.07%或2點，早段見3863，跌12點或0.31%，為全日低位，隨即節節上升，午後再向上突破，最高見3907點，升32點或0.83%，全日成交7167.42億元。一周累升14點或0.36%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指全日報13147，升140點或1.08%，今早開報13020.29點，漲0.11%或14點，早段低見12938，跌68點或0.52%，午後突破上午高位，最高見13164，升158點或1.21%，全日成交10090.29億元。一周累計升163點或1.26%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指全日報3109，升41點1.36%，今早開報3084.22點，漲0.55%或17點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300全日升41點或1.36%，報3109點，今早開報4547.91點，漲0.03%或1點。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">吳清人民日報撰文，稱提高資本市場制度的包容性適應性。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15482826-a%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e5%8d%87%e5%b9%85%e6%93%b4%e5%a4%a7-%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-14.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-05 15:25:30",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "韓股高收近2%　本周累計升4.4%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">韓股急升近2%收市。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">首爾綜合指數收報4100點，升71點，升幅1.78%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">韓股本周累計升4.4%。</p>\n</div>",
