            "title": "A股跌轉升  兩市成交9927億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股半日跌轉升，窄幅爭持，兩市合計成交9927.09億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-6.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-6.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證指數半日收報3878，升3點或0.08%，今早開報3873.12點，跌0.07%或2點，早段見3863，跌12點或0.31%，即節節上升，臨近收市高見3884，升9點或0.23%，為半日高位，半日成交4074.82億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日報13057，升50點或0.39%，今早開報13020.29點，漲0.11%或14點，早段低見12938，跌68點或0.52%，跌幅其後收窄，至中段倒升，最高見13084，升78點或0.6%，半日成交5852.27億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指半日報3082，升14點0.47%，今早開報3084.22點，漲0.55%或17點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300半日升14點或0.47%，報3082點，今早開報4547.91點，漲0.03%或1點。</p>\n</div>",
